'''Antoni Knot''' (born 1904, died 2 January 1982 in [[Wrocław]]) was a Polish scholar, historian, librarian and teacher. In 1929 he gained Ph.D. in Philosophy at the [[University of Lwów]]. In 1965 he became professor (''[[profesor zwyczajny]]'').<ref name=Knot>{{cite web|url=http://www.rocznikibiblioteczne.pl/redaktorzy.php?1 |title=Antoni Knot (1904-1982) |author=<!--Staff writer(s); no by-line.--> |date= |website=Roczniki Biblioteczne |publisher= |access-date= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150221232621/http://www.rocznikibiblioteczne.pl/redaktorzy.php?1 |archivedate=2015-02-21 }}</ref>

From 1947 to 1949 Knot was the chief librarian of [[Ossolineum]].<ref name=Knot/>

